			"text": "We revisit Levin 's theory about the correspondence of verb meaning and syntax ",
			"relation": "bg-goal"
		},
		{
			"id": 2,
			"parent": 1,
			"text": "and infer semantic classes from a large syntactic classification of more than 600 German verbs ",
